{
  "stem": "13063.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We are coming now to the year 1941.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We were banished from Krakow, myself, my mother, and my sister, because the German did not want to tolerate any Jews in Krakow itself.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we had to move to the suburbs of Krakow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At that time, it was about five miles, six miles from Krakow itself.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a little village called Borek [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Wielkopolski, ?] Borek, B-O-R-E-K.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When the Germans invaded Russia June 22, 1941, right away, they herded us back to Krakow, but not to our apartments, but to a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They established a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They walled off a portion [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] of a Krakow borough, which was called Podgolrze, P-O-D-G-O-- with a [INAUDIBLE]-- R-Z-E, Podgolrze.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You mean in the village?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were Jews who-- who took residence up-- who had to take up residence there, rent-- renting rooms from Poles who had spare rooms.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Many of our possessions just remained because we could-- what-- what could you put in one little room?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had one little room, myself, my sister, my-- and my-- my mother, one little room in-- in that village.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course, of course.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were watching.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody was watching, especially the Poles.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were trying to take advantage by selling us double the price produce and taking advantage in such a way that they should-- they should get as much profit as possible from the-- from the misfortune of the Jews.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, there were my cousins were in-- in Borek, some of my friends, and-- and a rabbi also was there, whom I adored, whom I studied with.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name was Levertov, Levertov, L-E-V-E-R-T-O-V, Levertov.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he and his family was there, also living in a-- in a room.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
